org.apache.gora.query

Interface Result<K,T extends Persistent>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccumuloResult, AvroResult, CassandraResult, CouchDBResult, DataFileAvroResult, DynamoDBResult, HBaseGetResult, HBaseResult, HBaseScannerResult, InfinispanResult, JCacheResult, MemStore.MemResult, MongoDBResult, ResultBase, ResultWSBase, SolrResult

    public interface Result<K,T extends Persistent>
    A result to a Query. Objects in the result set can be iterated by calling next(), get() and getKey().

    • Method Summary
